  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/8427ae091e8f8e1d18f9cdb3426e55d3.avif?t=1750114507\" width=620 height=176 /></span>This is a fun and hardcore roguelike platformer with a realistic ragdoll system for 1-5 players in which you have to reach the coveted reward by overcoming various traps! Only a few can make it through...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/6e01a85c566dede4a2c9f9063b831207.poster.avif?t=1750114507\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/6e01a85c566dede4a2c9f9063b831207.webm?t=1750114507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/6e01a85c566dede4a2c9f9063b831207.mp4?t=1750114507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The main rule of the game is to move forward, overcoming traps and obstacles, any falling into a trap will make you go through the path again - be careful!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/f037a5516d6e8234b877ce72c29b57e1.poster.avif?t=1750114507\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/f037a5516d6e8234b877ce72c29b57e1.webm?t=1750114507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/f037a5516d6e8234b877ce72c29b57e1.mp4?t=1750114507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>More than 10 characters are available to the player to choose from. The surrounding world has various weather effects, as well as a change of day and night. The character has a realistic ragdoll system, parkour and movement animation.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/8427ae091e8f8e1d18f9cdb3426e55d3.avif?t=1750114507\" width=620 height=176 /></span>This is a fun and hardcore roguelike platformer with a realistic ragdoll system for 1-5 players in which you have to reach the coveted reward by overcoming various traps! Only a few can make it through...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/6e01a85c566dede4a2c9f9063b831207.poster.avif?t=1750114507\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/6e01a85c566dede4a2c9f9063b831207.webm?t=1750114507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/6e01a85c566dede4a2c9f9063b831207.mp4?t=1750114507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The main rule of the game is to move forward, overcoming traps and obstacles, any falling into a trap will make you go through the path again - be careful!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/f037a5516d6e8234b877ce72c29b57e1.poster.avif?t=1750114507\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/f037a5516d6e8234b877ce72c29b57e1.webm?t=1750114507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067030/extras/f037a5516d6e8234b877ce72c29b57e1.mp4?t=1750114507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>More than 10 characters are available to the player to choose from. The surrounding world has various weather effects, as well as a change of day and night. The character has a realistic ragdoll system, parkour and movement animation.</p>",
